ActAn Act to amend certain Acts and to make certain consequential amendments (firearms)
SubjectOrder Fixing September 1, 2024 as the Day on Which Certain Provisions of An Act to amend certain Acts and to make certain consequential amendments (firearms) Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing September 1, 2024, as the day on which certain provisions of An Act to amend certain Acts and to make certain consequential amendments (firearms) COME INTO FORCE in order to bring into force date of the new Criminal Code definition of “firearm part” and consequential amendments to the Criminal Code.
